  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA26">
<l>vantit tavaṉai vaḻiniṉṟa vaimpūta</l>
<l>maintu makattaṭakki yārvamā – yuntip</l>
<l>paṭiyamarar vēlaiyāṉ paṇṭamarark kīnta</l>
<l>paṭiyamarar vāḻum pati</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Praising, restraining inside all five of the five senses</l>
<l>that were on the way to him, driving [them] affectionately,</l>
<l>the immortals of the earth will live in the abode given</l>
<l>of old to the immortals, because of [their] deeds as immortals by rank.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
